<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 15 of the Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The examination of veterinary drug residues referred in this Standard shall be marker residue, including the drug itself and its significant relevant metabolities.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The veterinary drug residue limits in foods shall meet the following Table. Veterinary drugs not listed in the Table shall not be detected. For those listed veterinary drugs not permitted to be used by Council of Agriculture, Executive Yuan shall only apply to the imported products.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard shall be implemented from the date of promulgation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
